|----------------|------------------|--------------------------------|
| Tools          | 8                | 6 (base + background_run + check)|
| Execution      | Blocking only    | Blocking + async child processes |
| Notification   | None             | Queue drained per loop         |
| Concurrency    | None             | Node.js `exec()` callbacks     |

